    "summary": "I'm a professional mentor and guide with a focus on personal and organizational growth, based in Amsterdam. I deliver workshops, seminars, and training sessions to a diverse array of professional environments and cultures. My objective is to guide individuals through their personal growth journeys and assist organizations in refining their culture, strategy, and operations for continuous improvement.\n\nI'm also involved in WeNeedDreams.com, an Amsterdam-based initiative striving to visualize and share possible systemic solutions to global problems. By uniting thinkers, dreamers, and makers, we aim to change the narrative, inspiring optimism and action towards resolving pressing issues.\n\nPreviously, I provided transformative leadership to LEKKER Bikes & Boats, guiding the company from its initial struggles to becoming a professional, refocused scale-up. Prior to that, I founded Flare - Partners in Innovation, a strategy agency dedicated to facilitating meaningful growth and innovation across various industries.",
